beyond the hills ( romanian : dupÄƒ dealuri ) is a 2012 romanian drama film directed by cristian mungiu , starring cristina flutur and cosmina stratan . the narrative follows two young women at an orthodox convent in romania . the film premiered at the 2012 cannes film festival , where mungiu won the award for best screenplay , and flutur and stratan shared the award for best actress . it was selected as the romanian entry for the best foreign language oscar at the 85th academy awards , making the january shortlist .